Subject: [TRIVIAL] [CI] resolve merge conflict with upstream in build-manywheel-images.yml
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

resolve merge conflict between the local branch and upstream/main in
.github/workflows/build-manywheel-images.yml

Upstream changes that caused the conflict:
- Dropped cuda12.8 and cuda12.9 aarch64 build matrix entries (PRs #179158, #181273)
- Changed the aarch64 CUDA runner from linux.arm64.2xlarge.ephemeral to
  linux.arm64.m7g.4xlarge.ephemeral (PR #179158)

Resolution:
- Drop the local manylinux2_28_aarch64-builder cuda12.8 and cuda12.9 entries
  to match upstream's surviving CUDA aarch64 set (cuda13.2, cuda13.0, cuda12.6)
- Update the local manylinux2_28_aarch64-builder cuda* entries to use the new
  larger runner (linux.arm64.m7g.4xlarge.ephemeral) introduced upstream

Self-assessment: TRIVIAL
